
** Monitoring

  xm top

  xm info

  xm log

  xm dmesg

  xm list [-l] [<domid>]

  xm consoe <domid>
Exit with C+]
See also vncviewer

  xm start    <domname>
  xm pause    <domid>
  xm unpause  <domid>
  xm reboot   <domid>
  xm resume   <domname>
  xm suspend
  xm shutdown 
  xm destroy  <domid>
